 And this I think is an important gap in the literature

52:02.080 --> 52:04.400
 that ought to be filled, whether or not, for instance,

52:04.400 --> 52:06.320
 high intensity interval training,

52:06.320 --> 52:08.640
 or whether or not weight training,

