 on these focused attention tasks

56:17.120 --> 56:21.800
 compared to a group that watched videos

56:21.800 --> 56:23.520
 for the exercise period.

56:23.520 --> 56:25.160
 This was an hour and a half.

56:25.160 --> 56:29.160
 For the exercise period, this was an hour of cycling

