 It's very, very important.

57:26.040 --> 57:27.800
 I don't think I've ever mentioned this on the podcast,

57:27.800 --> 57:30.720
 which is any kind of physical activity

57:30.720 --> 57:34.000
 will increase cortisol to varying degrees.

